=head1 DESCRIPTION

Configures the firewall policy deployment model of Network Firewall.
For information about Network Firewall deployment models, see Network
Firewall example architectures with routing
(https://docs.aws.amazon.com/network-firewall/latest/developerguide/architectures.html)
in the I<Network Firewall Developer Guide>.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 FirewallDeploymentModel => Str

Defines the deployment model to use for the firewall policy. To use a
distributed model, set PolicyOption
(https://docs.aws.amazon.com/fms/2018-01-01/APIReference/API_PolicyOption.html)
to C<NULL>.



